@startuml
skinparam titleFontSize 24
skinparam titleFontStyle bold
skinparam monochrome true
title Landing Page Content State Transition

[*] --> Draft : Content created

Draft --> UnderReview : Submitted for approval
Draft --> Archived : Draft discarded

UnderReview --> Approved : Admin approves
UnderReview --> Draft : Needs revision

Approved --> Published : Content goes live

Published --> UnderReview : Needs update/edit
Published --> Archived : Content removed

Archived --> Draft : Content restored
Archived --> [*] : Permanently deleted

Draft : Being edited
Draft : Not visible to public
Draft : Can be modified freely

UnderReview : Awaiting approval
UnderReview : Cannot be edited
UnderReview : Admin reviewing

Published : Live on website
Published : Visible to public
Published : Can be updated

Archived : Removed from site
Archived : Hidden from public
Archived : Can be restored

@enduml
